        <span class="img"><img src="/media/frettir-2018/medium/Hola-vid-Gljufura-minni.jpg" alt="Slitlagsskemmdir - Gljúfurá" /></span>


      <h3>

        <span class="meta">
          
          

          <span class='date'>7.3.2018</span>
          

          <span class="stream">:</span>
        </span>

          <a class="atitle" href="/about/news/the-weather-and-potholes">The weather and potholes</a>

      </h3>
      

      <div class="summary">

         
             When winter releases it firm grip these weeks in Iceland the paved roads get a beating. Because of the weather conditions potholes and other fractures in the paved surface can occur fairly quickly. Therefore it is a reason to drive extra carefully with this in mind.
         
         

        <span class="more"><a href="/about/news/the-weather-and-potholes" title="The weather and potholes">Read more</a></span>


      </div>

      

    </div>

    <div class="item itm2" data-aid="19348">

        <span class="img"><img src="/media/frettir-2017/medium/Sveinn3.jpg" alt="Við Steinavötn 3.10.2017" /></span>


      <h3>

        <span class="meta">
          
          

          <span class='date'>3.10.2017</span>
          

          <span class="stream">:</span>
        </span>

          <a class="atitle" href="/about/news/the-temporary-bridge-over-steinavotn-opened-tomorrow">The temporary bridge over Steinavötn opens tomorrow</a>

      </h3>
      

      <div class="summary">

         
             <p>The work building the 104 m temporary bridge over Steinavötn in Southeast Iceland went so well that it will be opened well ahead of schedule. It will be opened tomorrow at noon, Wednesday 4th October for all traffic.</p>
         
         

        <span class="more"><a href="/about/news/the-temporary-bridge-over-steinavotn-opened-tomorrow" title="The temporary bridge over Steinavötn opens tomorrow">Read more</a></span>


